WEBVTT

00:00:07.610 --> 00:00:14.490
<font face="Times New Roman" size="30"><b>The Apothecary <font color="#000000">Diaries</font></b></font>

00:01:28.270 --> 00:01:29.980
<font face="Times New Roman" size="30"><b>{\an3}<font size="24">The Apothecary <font color="#000000">Diaries</font></font></b></font>

00:01:31.020 --> 00:01:33.980
<font size="10">{\an1}This story is a work of fiction. The names of all of the characters, organizations, and so on
 are imaginary. It also bears no connection to any specific real-life events.</font>

00:01:35.970 --> 00:01:37.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That girl bumped into the eunuch,</font>

00:01:37.820 --> 00:01:40.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and he dropped the ice 
he was carrying for a concubine.</font>

00:01:40.050 --> 00:01:41.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I feel sorry for her.</font>

00:01:41.740 --> 00:01:45.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Shouldn't you feel sorry for the eunuch 
who was carrying the ice?</font>

00:01:45.870 --> 00:01:48.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's hope he gets away with <i>just</i> a caning.</font>

00:01:50.170 --> 00:01:53.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I-I'm sorry—</font>

00:01:53.170 --> 00:01:55.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please excuse us, we weren't paying attention!</font>

00:01:55.880 --> 00:01:58.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You think "sorry" will cut it?!</font>

00:01:58.670 --> 00:02:01.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I can't wash this and pretend nothing happened!</font>

00:02:01.340 --> 00:02:02.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We don't have any replacements!</font>

00:02:06.330 --> 00:02:08.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Dammit... What do I do?!</font>

00:02:10.110 --> 00:02:12.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Ice is precious this time of year.</i></font>

00:02:12.320 --> 00:02:14.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>You could buy a person with it.</i></font>

00:02:20.150 --> 00:02:22.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Which concubine was this ice for?</i></font>

00:02:22.920 --> 00:02:26.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Concubine Loulan! She wanted some icy 
treats for cooling her off in the afternoon!</font>

00:02:28.430 --> 00:02:30.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Out of all of them, it's one 
I have no connections with.</i></font>

00:02:33.480 --> 00:02:36.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What do we do? We can't pay for it.</i></font>

00:02:36.320 --> 00:02:38.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It would be terrible to anger 
a high-ranking concubine.</i></font>

00:02:39.720 --> 00:02:42.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If we could at least 
find something to replace it...</i></font>

00:02:44.410 --> 00:02:46.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Can we have this ice?</font>

00:02:46.610 --> 00:02:47.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Do whatever you want!</font>

00:02:48.420 --> 00:02:52.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In that case, I'll use this 
to make something else.</font>

00:02:52.370 --> 00:02:55.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Could you pass that along
 to Concubine Loulan?</font>

00:02:56.550 --> 00:03:00.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Try it, if you can. You have less than an hour!</font>

00:03:01.050 --> 00:03:02.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Understood.</font>

00:03:02.650 --> 00:03:04.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I might have exactly enough time.</i></font>

00:03:04.330 --> 00:03:07.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But I don't even know if 
the other ingredients are available.</i></font>

00:03:07.480 --> 00:03:10.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I have to use what I can to—</i></font>

00:03:14.210 --> 00:03:16.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>W-Why is he here?</i></font>

00:03:18.340 --> 00:03:20.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>There's no time to dwell on that!</i></font>

00:03:29.850 --> 00:03:33.770
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20">{\an3}Episode 39: Ice</font>

00:03:32.310 --> 00:03:35.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}What do I do, Maomao?!</font>

00:03:37.020 --> 00:03:39.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh, poor girl.</font>

00:03:43.320 --> 00:03:45.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>A concubine gave her a hair stick,</i></font>

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:48.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>so she was happily 
admiring it while walking, and...</i></font>

00:03:48.700 --> 00:03:53.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I wonder if that concubine likes me!</font>

00:03:53.540 --> 00:03:56.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She wants me to give her 
another massage sometime!</font>

00:03:57.160 --> 00:03:58.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Good for you.</font>

00:03:59.820 --> 00:04:03.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>After the last time, Xiaolan continued 
to work on building connections.</i></font>

00:04:03.430 --> 00:04:07.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She was just telling me how she scored 
a direct request from a low-ranked concubine.</i></font>

00:04:07.730 --> 00:04:10.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I heard she was sold off by her parents,</i></font>

00:04:10.090 --> 00:04:12.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>but I've never seen her look glum, even once.</i></font>

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:15.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She must have been so happy.</i></font>

00:04:18.980 --> 00:04:23.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Getting yelled at like that must have 
made her so scared, she couldn't move.</i></font>

00:04:34.740 --> 00:04:36.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is there something you need?</font>

00:04:36.210 --> 00:04:39.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">May I borrow a kitchen and some ingredients?</font>

00:04:39.210 --> 00:04:43.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How brazen. And what do I get in return?</font>

00:04:44.770 --> 00:04:48.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Don't toy with me, I don't have time!</i></font>

00:04:49.390 --> 00:04:52.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I have nothing to give you in return.</font>

00:04:53.370 --> 00:04:54.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But I must ask regardless!</font>

00:04:55.810 --> 00:04:59.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I couldn't be more out of line, 
but this isn't the time to worry about it.</i></font>

00:05:01.810 --> 00:05:04.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You didn't cause that situation, did you?</font>

00:05:06.150 --> 00:05:07.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're right.</font>

00:05:08.770 --> 00:05:13.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She was originally just someone 
who was a good source of gossip.</i></font>

00:05:13.900 --> 00:05:18.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Even for that, I gave her snacks in exchange, 
so we owe each other nothing.</i></font>

00:05:21.690 --> 00:05:23.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I'm not obligated to help her.</i></font>

00:05:24.760 --> 00:05:25.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But...</i></font>

00:05:26.870 --> 00:05:29.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I wouldn't sleep well if I didn't help.</font>

00:05:36.260 --> 00:05:38.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see. You won't sleep well, is that it?</font>

00:05:38.850 --> 00:05:41.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. It would affect my work for the next day.</font>

00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:43.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We certainly can't have that.</font>

00:05:47.340 --> 00:05:49.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Fine, but there's one condition.</font>

00:05:54.770 --> 00:05:58.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">When someone is talking to you, 
let them finish and pay attention.</font>

00:06:01.080 --> 00:06:03.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's all?</font>

00:06:04.630 --> 00:06:07.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You can't even do that much.</font>

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:14.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Never mind then, I'll think of 
something else. What should it be?</font>

00:06:15.310 --> 00:06:16.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I have a bad feeling about this!</i></font>

00:06:17.290 --> 00:06:19.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Should I rely on Lady Gyokuyou instead?</i></font>

00:06:19.900 --> 00:06:23.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>No, I can't ask for her help on something 
related to Concubine Loulan.</i></font>

00:06:32.380 --> 00:06:34.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Thank you.</font>

00:06:34.260 --> 00:06:37.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Don't you wear a hair stick?</font>

00:06:37.130 --> 00:06:40.120
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The other Jade Pavilion
 ladies-in-waiting are more fashionable.</font>

00:06:40.440 --> 00:06:43.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You say that, but I don't have any accessories.</font>

00:06:43.860 --> 00:06:46.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I gave you one at the garden party, remember?</font>

00:06:47.290 --> 00:06:49.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Don't tell me you sold it off.</font>

00:06:49.780 --> 00:06:51.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I haven't.</font>

00:06:51.240 --> 00:06:52.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Not yet, anyway.</i></font>

00:06:55.850 --> 00:06:57.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wear that, then.</font>

00:06:59.100 --> 00:07:00.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is that all?</font>

00:07:01.140 --> 00:07:02.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is there a problem?</font>

00:07:05.140 --> 00:07:08.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">When you wear it, I'll tell you.</font>

00:07:11.390 --> 00:07:13.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A kitchen, yes? I'll have someone prepare it.</font>

00:07:25.260 --> 00:07:26.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I brought it!</font>

00:07:27.830 --> 00:07:29.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please place it there.</font>

00:07:29.700 --> 00:07:30.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Got it.</font>

00:07:32.050 --> 00:07:33.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maomao, is this...</font>

00:07:36.430 --> 00:07:40.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Sugar and fruits and... Cow milk?</font>

00:07:40.850 --> 00:07:45.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm glad they had fresh milk, 
it goes bad pretty fast.</font>

00:07:45.810 --> 00:07:50.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Can you really make something 
like an ice treat out of these?</font>

00:07:50.080 --> 00:07:51.120
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I think so.</font>

00:07:51.850 --> 00:07:54.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I've only watched it being made once, though.</i></font>

00:07:55.180 --> 00:07:57.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm counting on you, really!</font>

00:07:57.380 --> 00:07:59.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'll call you when it's done.</font>

00:08:07.950 --> 00:08:09.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Stir this up.</font>

00:08:09.450 --> 00:08:10.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">R-Right!</font>

00:08:16.010 --> 00:08:17.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What are you doing?!</font>

00:08:17.530 --> 00:08:18.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Crushing the ice.</font>

00:08:18.890 --> 00:08:21.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wow, so small...</font>

00:08:21.690 --> 00:08:22.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Don't worry.</font>

00:08:29.100 --> 00:08:30.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Good.</font>

00:08:30.760 --> 00:08:31.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Salt?</font>

00:08:32.030 --> 00:08:34.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Xiaolan, put your bowl in here.</font>

00:08:34.960 --> 00:08:35.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes!</font>

00:08:46.910 --> 00:08:48.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What? No way.</font>

00:08:50.670 --> 00:08:52.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's starting to harden!</font>

00:08:52.380 --> 00:08:55.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Xiaolan, cut up the fruit. Tiny pieces, okay?</font>

00:08:55.040 --> 00:08:56.430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Y-Yeah!</font>

00:08:58.660 --> 00:09:04.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Add fruits, mix some more, 
and place it in the bowl...</font>

00:09:08.120 --> 00:09:09.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is it finished?!</font>

00:09:09.730 --> 00:09:11.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hey, is this...</font>

00:09:11.470 --> 00:09:13.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yep, it's an ice treat.</font>

00:09:15.740 --> 00:09:17.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It should do for now.</i></font>

00:09:17.860 --> 00:09:22.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If I had more time, I could have added 
eggs or scented it with herbs, too.</i></font>

00:09:23.190 --> 00:09:24.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's get this to her right away.</font>

00:09:24.730 --> 00:09:26.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yeah, but...</font>

00:09:27.180 --> 00:09:29.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Shouldn't we taste it first?</font>

00:09:30.590 --> 00:09:33.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Back to her usual self.</i></font>

00:09:36.380 --> 00:09:37.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There are some leftovers.</font>

00:09:39.990 --> 00:09:43.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Mmm, delicious!</font>

00:09:43.380 --> 00:09:45.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What? Hey, is it done?!</font>

00:09:46.540 --> 00:09:47.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please deliver this.</font>

00:09:49.800 --> 00:09:51.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Are you sure it's good enough for—</font>

00:09:55.230 --> 00:09:56.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Do you see any issues with it?</font>

00:09:59.140 --> 00:10:00.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">To Concubine Loulan, quickly, please.</font>

00:10:00.770 --> 00:10:02.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">G-Got it!</font>

00:10:04.910 --> 00:10:08.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm so glad! Thanks, Maomao!</font>

00:10:09.160 --> 00:10:12.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I don't know. I hope Concubine Loulan likes it.</font>

00:10:13.640 --> 00:10:15.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Don't be mean!</font>

00:10:15.670 --> 00:10:21.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Boo! Bonk, bonk, bonk...</font>

00:10:16.180 --> 00:10:19.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Master Jinshi told me 
about her likes and dislikes.</i></font>

00:10:19.690 --> 00:10:21.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She'll take a taste, at least, for sure.</i></font>

00:10:22.060 --> 00:10:26.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Come on! Anyway, let's eat 
the rest before it melts.</font>

00:10:26.020 --> 00:10:28.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yeah, let's eat it!</font>

00:10:28.330 --> 00:10:29.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Shisui!</font>

00:10:29.540 --> 00:10:30.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What are you doing here?</font>

00:10:30.900 --> 00:10:35.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I heard the commotion, 
so I ditched work and came over.</font>

00:10:35.790 --> 00:10:37.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're so bad!</font>

00:10:40.490 --> 00:10:42.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This is delicious!</font>

00:10:43.020 --> 00:10:47.120
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Come on, don't just take the best part.</font>

00:10:53.610 --> 00:10:55.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Mine!</font>

00:10:54.370 --> 00:10:59.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Come on! Don't take it all!</font>

00:10:57.010 --> 00:10:59.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Mine, all mine!</font>

00:11:00.540 --> 00:11:02.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I'm gonna need more of this.</i></font>

00:11:02.520 --> 00:11:04.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Come on!</font>

00:11:04.350 --> 00:11:06.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh! You caught me!</font>

00:11:06.940 --> 00:11:08.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Or maybe not!</font>

00:11:06.940 --> 00:11:09.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Maybe I have enough for one more batch.</i></font>

00:11:10.100 --> 00:11:11.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wait up!</font>

00:11:11.310 --> 00:11:12.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Okay, open up!</font>

00:11:13.630 --> 00:11:16.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Mmm, so delicious!</font>

00:11:17.610 --> 00:11:21.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Your turn next, Shisui. Open up!</font>

00:11:31.290 --> 00:11:34.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh, it's moving.</font>

00:11:43.870 --> 00:11:46.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lingli, do you want to touch?</font>

00:12:01.780 --> 00:12:04.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She's going to give birth soon.</i></font>

00:12:13.890 --> 00:12:16.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Everything seems good, for now.</i></font>

00:12:17.190 --> 00:12:18.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's strange.</font>

00:12:18.630 --> 00:12:22.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Unlike with Lingli, 
this one only kicks downwards.</font>

00:12:23.400 --> 00:12:24.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Down?</font>

00:12:24.610 --> 00:12:27.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I guess quirks come out this early.</font>

00:12:34.670 --> 00:12:37.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">May I touch, just a little?</font>

00:12:38.660 --> 00:12:40.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, sure.</font>

00:12:41.260 --> 00:12:42.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Excuse me.</font>

00:12:54.570 --> 00:12:57.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How did Princess Lingli's delivery go?</font>

00:12:57.630 --> 00:13:01.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It was really easy, especially 
considering it was her first time.</font>

00:13:01.420 --> 00:13:05.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maybe it helped that her body was rather small.</font>

00:13:05.390 --> 00:13:07.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Who assisted with the delivery?</font>

00:13:07.010 --> 00:13:09.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I did.</font>

00:13:09.080 --> 00:13:11.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I don't trust the doctors here,</font>

00:13:11.380 --> 00:13:15.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and the court lady we hired 
for the delivery became ill.</font>

00:13:16.200 --> 00:13:18.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I did a lot of studying 
beforehand, so it worked out.</font>

00:13:19.210 --> 00:13:22.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, will you be requesting
 that court lady again?</font>

00:13:22.060 --> 00:13:26.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No, I don't want her to fall ill 
at the worst time again.</font>

00:13:27.090 --> 00:13:30.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I heard Concubine Lihua also had 
someone else come in when giving birth.</font>

00:13:30.730 --> 00:13:34.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A midwife who temporarily 
entered the rear palace, originally.</font>

00:13:34.900 --> 00:13:36.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see...</font>

00:13:37.410 --> 00:13:41.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Are they bringing someone 
from outside the rear palace again?</i></font>

00:13:41.010 --> 00:13:43.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Even if Lady Hongniang assisted last time,</i></font>

00:13:43.000 --> 00:13:45.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>she's not a professional in the field.</i></font>

00:13:47.540 --> 00:13:49.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If you have a concern, please let it out.</font>

00:13:53.560 --> 00:13:58.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I can't say for certain, 
but this could be a breech delivery.</font>

00:13:59.650 --> 00:14:00.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A breech delivery?</font>

00:14:01.190 --> 00:14:05.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, the kicking downwards suggests as much.</font>

00:14:06.050 --> 00:14:11.120
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If Princess Lingli was kicking upwards, 
her head must have been facing down.</font>

00:14:11.730 --> 00:14:16.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A baby delivery goes most smoothly when 
the head, the largest part, comes out first.</font>

00:14:17.300 --> 00:14:20.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In contrast, when the feet, 
which are smallest, come out first,</font>

00:14:20.420 --> 00:14:23.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">it drastically increases the risks 
associated with the birth.</font>

00:14:28.130 --> 00:14:30.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Are you sure it's a breech delivery?</font>

00:14:30.980 --> 00:14:33.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's just a possibility.</font>

00:14:33.310 --> 00:14:37.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If I can examine a bit more thoroughly, 
I might know more.</font>

00:14:37.910 --> 00:14:39.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Can you?</font>

00:14:41.560 --> 00:14:46.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I can't say for sure. My dad only 
taught me about medicine.</i></font>

00:14:47.460 --> 00:14:49.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Everything else is just 
things I've observed.</i></font>

00:14:50.740 --> 00:14:51.870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Do it, please.</font>

00:14:58.040 --> 00:15:00.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">By they way, by "examine," I mean...</font>

00:15:02.540 --> 00:15:04.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh, is that so?</font>

00:15:06.620 --> 00:15:10.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's nothing compared to delivering her.</font>

00:15:12.100 --> 00:15:14.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Mothers are strong, I guess.</i></font>

00:15:18.570 --> 00:15:19.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Understood.</font>

00:15:33.290 --> 00:15:34.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How was it?</font>

00:15:34.720 --> 00:15:36.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>This is a hard thing to say, but...</i></font>

00:15:38.250 --> 00:15:40.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It seems quite likely.</font>

00:15:42.100 --> 00:15:45.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Sometimes they just change direction 
on their own before birth,</font>

00:15:45.440 --> 00:15:47.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but given how little time there is left...</font>

00:15:50.290 --> 00:15:51.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What should we do?</font>

00:15:52.140 --> 00:15:57.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In the pleasure district, I heard 
moxibustion and good exercise is helpful.</font>

00:15:58.790 --> 00:16:00.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I can help with moxibustion.</font>

00:16:00.480 --> 00:16:02.120
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please.</font>

00:16:02.120 --> 00:16:06.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'll ask around outside the rear palace 
for anything else that might help.</font>

00:16:06.890 --> 00:16:07.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes.</font>

00:16:10.280 --> 00:16:15.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What happens if it ends up 
being a breech delivery?</font>

00:16:16.730 --> 00:16:19.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We might need to cut into your belly.</font>

00:16:20.420 --> 00:16:21.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see.</font>

00:16:21.960 --> 00:16:23.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Gyokuyou...</font>

00:16:24.190 --> 00:16:27.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But if we do that, 
Lady Gyokuyou's life would be at risk.</i></font>

00:16:28.350 --> 00:16:31.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's risky enough even with a proper midwife.</i></font>

00:16:32.420 --> 00:16:35.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If only the quack was a proper doctor...</i></font>

00:16:35.410 --> 00:16:37.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But who else can replace him?</i></font>

00:16:40.890 --> 00:16:44.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>To enter the rear palace, 
a doctor has to be castrated.</i></font>

00:16:45.170 --> 00:16:48.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But where can we find a good 
doctor who's also a eunuch—</i></font>

00:16:49.100 --> 00:16:52.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>There is. The perfect candidate.</i></font>

00:16:52.860 --> 00:16:53.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But...</i></font>

00:16:55.180 --> 00:16:56.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maomao?</font>

00:16:58.370 --> 00:17:00.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I do know of someone.</font>

00:17:01.770 --> 00:17:02.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You do?</font>

00:17:02.910 --> 00:17:05.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Someone with outstanding skills as a doctor,</font>

00:17:05.580 --> 00:17:08.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and also has experience 
delivering babies by incision.</font>

00:17:09.050 --> 00:17:10.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh.</font>

00:17:10.180 --> 00:17:12.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Really? Ah...</font>

00:17:12.900 --> 00:17:16.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Could it be... 
Master Jinshi's lady-in-waiting...</font>

00:17:16.540 --> 00:17:18.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No. He's a doctor.</font>

00:17:20.770 --> 00:17:23.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What in the world did Lady Suiren do?</i></font>

00:17:24.280 --> 00:17:25.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Who is this person?</font>

00:17:26.250 --> 00:17:30.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He was once exiled from the rear palace.</font>

00:17:30.990 --> 00:17:32.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A criminal.</font>

00:17:34.280 --> 00:17:35.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Unacceptable!</font>

00:17:35.860 --> 00:17:39.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Gyokuyou and 
the baby's lives are at stake.</font>

00:17:39.130 --> 00:17:41.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It needs to be someone trustworthy!</font>

00:17:41.030 --> 00:17:44.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He <i>is</i> trustworthy! 
He's the best doctor in this nation.</font>

00:17:47.240 --> 00:17:51.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Those are some big words, rare from you.</font>

00:17:51.330 --> 00:17:52.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But he's still a criminal, right?</font>

00:17:54.260 --> 00:17:55.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There's just no way.</font>

00:17:55.840 --> 00:17:56.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But—</font>

00:17:56.700 --> 00:17:58.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wait, both of you.</font>

00:17:58.690 --> 00:18:01.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hongniang, don't stop her 
before she's finished.</font>

00:18:01.630 --> 00:18:04.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maomao, please calm down and explain.</font>

00:18:09.030 --> 00:18:11.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What crime did he commit?</font>

00:18:11.890 --> 00:18:15.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This person is a eunuch, 
and was a doctor in the rear palace.</font>

00:18:16.950 --> 00:18:20.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In the past, he helped deliver 
the emperor, the current crown prince,</font>

00:18:20.530 --> 00:18:24.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and Concubine Ah-Duo's baby.</font>

00:18:24.900 --> 00:18:30.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">As for the reason for his exile, all I know 
is that it's related to Concubine Ah-Duo.</font>

00:18:31.210 --> 00:18:36.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's not like he actually told me, 
or that I know all the facts for sure.</i></font>

00:18:36.260 --> 00:18:38.380
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}...Luomen, expelled...</b></font>

00:18:37.190 --> 00:18:40.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>There are some records, 
but most of it is conjecture.</i></font>

00:18:41.850 --> 00:18:45.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What is his relation to you, Maomao?</font>

00:18:45.810 --> 00:18:49.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He is my adopted father, and the person 
who taught me the ways of the apothecary.</font>

00:18:54.150 --> 00:18:55.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I understand.</font>

00:18:55.420 --> 00:18:58.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's ask Master Jinshi 
if we can bring that person in.</font>

00:18:59.700 --> 00:19:00.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Gyokuyou!</font>

00:19:01.220 --> 00:19:04.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hongniang, I want to consult someone 
who's a real professional.</font>

00:19:05.550 --> 00:19:07.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It would be best if it's someone we can trust.</font>

00:19:08.700 --> 00:19:11.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Besides, I just can't believe 
he's a bad person.</font>

00:19:11.980 --> 00:19:15.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Look at how this stray cat respects him.</font>

00:19:15.830 --> 00:19:16.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Stray cat...?</i></font>

00:19:16.800 --> 00:19:18.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But he's a criminal!</font>

00:19:18.440 --> 00:19:19.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hongniang,</font>

00:19:19.880 --> 00:19:23.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm sure you've also heard the stories 
about the rear palace back then.</font>

00:19:24.590 --> 00:19:29.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So many lives were tossed around 
by the reign of the great empress.</font>

00:19:29.970 --> 00:19:33.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We can't judge "crimes" 
from back then at face value.</font>

00:19:37.620 --> 00:19:38.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Understood.</font>

00:19:39.310 --> 00:19:44.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In that case, I have a letter to write.</font>

00:19:44.610 --> 00:19:46.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That's what I call dignity.</i></font>

00:19:46.910 --> 00:19:50.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I guess that's what a concubine 
becoming a mother is like.</i></font>

00:19:53.180 --> 00:19:55.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Two days after speaking to Lady Gyokuyou...</i></font>

00:19:59.270 --> 00:20:00.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Thank you.</font>

00:20:01.720 --> 00:20:04.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We've been eagerly awaiting 
your arrival, Master Luomen.</font>

00:20:17.390 --> 00:20:23.430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, well. Who would've thought 
I'd come back here?</font>

00:20:23.430 --> 00:20:27.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>A man, who looked more like an elderly 
woman, arrived at the rear palace.</i></font>

00:20:30.930 --> 00:20:32.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I am Luomen.</font>

00:20:33.510 --> 00:20:39.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I will be temporarily serving in
 the rear palace's medical office.</font>

00:20:39.090 --> 00:20:43.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I've heard from Maomao. 
Thank you for your help.</font>

00:20:43.470 --> 00:20:44.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes.</font>

00:20:48.100 --> 00:20:52.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Temporarily? Well, that makes sense, I guess.</i></font>

00:20:53.150 --> 00:20:56.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I was a bit worried 
that the quack would get fired.</i></font>

00:20:56.480 --> 00:20:58.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Good to know I don't have to worry about that.</i></font>

00:20:58.740 --> 00:21:00.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well then, please excuse me.</font>

00:21:03.540 --> 00:21:04.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please.</font>

00:21:04.270 --> 00:21:05.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes.</font>

00:21:10.870 --> 00:21:15.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hey! That's your father, right?</font>

00:21:15.250 --> 00:21:17.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, sort of.</font>

00:21:17.090 --> 00:21:19.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Technically, he's my great uncle.</i></font>

00:21:19.750 --> 00:21:23.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He's not at all what we imagined.</font>

00:21:24.150 --> 00:21:27.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He seems gentle and calm.</font>

00:21:27.340 --> 00:21:29.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, like a normal person.</font>

00:21:29.840 --> 00:21:33.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's like, did he really raise Maomao?</font>

00:21:33.140 --> 00:21:34.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">My thoughts exactly.</font>

00:21:38.490 --> 00:21:40.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">All of you...!</font>

00:21:40.190 --> 00:21:41.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh, I mean...</font>

00:21:41.570 --> 00:21:43.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What were you imagining,?</font>

00:21:43.950 --> 00:21:47.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well... you know...</font>

00:21:48.120 --> 00:21:49.870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He seems like he has common sense.</font>

00:21:49.870 --> 00:21:51.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Exactly.</font>

00:21:53.960 --> 00:21:55.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I don't get it.</i></font>

00:23:45.020 --> 00:23:59.950
<font face="Times New Roman" size="22">{\an7}Next Time</font>

00:23:56.220 --> 00:23:59.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>{\an8}Next time:
 "Festering Resentment."</i></font>

00:23:56.240 --> 00:23:59.950
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20">{\an3}Episode 40: Festering Resentment</font>

